{"type": "article", "id": 21470, "title": "带纺织面料的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-29T07:33:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061402153xOVvUqgoCQwS5fu.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是丹麦设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 推出的 2016 年新品，其中的椅子设计都带有纺织面料的座位。它们分为有扶手、无扶手和类似高脚凳三种，颜色单一，靠背和座位面是连在一体的，形成柔和的弧形，简洁轻盈。因为纺织面料多了一份居家的生活气息。<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150952Dt1hIpNYLyAkRMis.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150953Y59IOHJcTqaeSmwp.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509533IlaLrMBVZeDPwWH.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150954ShAo8ulZ5zFnMN62.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}